lead_paragraph: Defending champion Andy Sullivan had 10 birdies in a 10-under round of 61 to take a share of the lead after two rounds of the Portugal Masters on Friday.

headline.print_headline: Andy Sullivan Joins Marc Warren as Portugal Masters Leaders
